                     <interp inst="t18320405-66-person679" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
            . I <rs id="t18320405-66-viclabel416" type="occupation">keep a cheesemonger's-shop</rs>
                  <join result="persNameOccupation" targOrder="Y" targets="t18320405-66-victim677 t18320405-66-viclabel416"></join>. This pork was in my window; Waller came in, and I missed it - he produced it: I knew it, as it was the only one I had; I had not seen the prisoner.</p>
